:"这次事件充分体现了bgm设计的优越性<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">条目吐槽箱没有点赞或者踩的功能，更不像猫眼之类的短评都可以被他人回复，杜绝了多少撕逼啊...真的每一处细节都可以看出站长的良苦用心和高瞻远瞩<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/52/5298.jpg","floor":"#23-1","id":"1421606","time":"2019-2-17 02:19","userId":"taxet","userName":"名媛小百合✅官方认证","userSign":"","message":"（其实就是懒）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#23-2","id":"1423168","time":"2019-2-21 20:00","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">名媛小百合</span> 说: （其实就是懒）</q></div>这是艺术！是懒的艺术啊！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/79/317972.jpg","floor":"#24","id":"1421141","time":"2019-2-15 14:49","userId":"317972","userName":"Destiny4073","userSign":"","message":"看s1都是讨伐豆瓣，来bgm又是另一番景象了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/58/5881.jpg","floor":"#25","id":"1421171","time":"2019-2-15 16:06","userId":"w","userName":"如月千早","userSign":"","message":"又不是票房警察，有啥用","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/60/106075.jpg","floor":"#26","id":"1421416","time":"2019-2-16 09:06","userId":"needxuyao","userName":"XN","userSign":"","message":"到处都是踩豆瓣的，这儿能多少理解和同情豆瓣，大概是同是评分网站用户群有重合的原因。实际上网络社区的意识形态都有明显的偏向，与现实社会社区的组成有很大差异，在输出观点时只能代表特定群体，即使做统计也很难有普遍的社会学价值。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/52/5298.jpg","floor":"#27","id":"1421607","time":"2019-2-17 02:22","userId":"taxet","userName":"名媛小百合✅官方认证","userSign":"(双目失明丝毫不影响我上BGM)","message":"个人的极端评价是不会影响一部作品的整体评分的，只有刷分才会。<br>艺术作品评价的主观性本来就很重，你喜欢的作品别人不喜欢或者你不喜欢的作品别人喜欢是很常有的事。这种评分作为观赏之前的参考没什么问题，但是观赏之后这个评分对你个人来说其实也就没什么意义了，你自己的评分才是最重要的。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/26/442614.jpg","floor":"#28","id":"1421608","time":"2019-2-17 02:40","userId":"longlivel5i","userName":"trivedy","userSign":"","message":"流浪地球这个问题建议分开看。它涉及到意识形态，和一般的撕逼事件不同，源头根本不是电影本身。流浪地球（我不太喜欢\"小破球\"这个叫法<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">）成了两派用来党同伐异的牺牲品。所以讨论电影到底值多少分根本毫无意义。所谓的警察也并不是评分警察，只是站队警察。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#28-1","id":"1421609","time":"2019-2-17 02:44","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"新一轮文革开始了的标志。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#29","id":"1421851","time":"2019-2-17 21:29","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"看到篇微博文章<br><a href=\"https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404340436318683469\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404340436318683469</a><br><a href=\"https://media.weibo.cn/article?id=2309404340436318683469&jumpfrom=weibocom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://media.weibo.cn/article?i ... p;jumpfrom=weibocom</a><br>数据分析<br><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SaVHJ_DwgmWqOi-_8-yMiQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SaVHJ_DwgmWqOi-_8-yMiQ</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/53/315316.jpg","floor":"#30","id":"1423166","time":"2019-2-21 19:52","userId":"yikaicheng","userName":"泽渡真琴","userSign":"(好大的关东煮)","message":"对付恶意打一星的评分水军一刀剁了他们亲妈不好么？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#30-1","id":"1423167","time":"2019-2-21 19:55","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"人家打了个一分，你就要杀人亲妈，这就是战争的真相。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/45/124586.jpg","floor":"#31","id":"1423232","time":"2019-2-21 22:45","userId":"124586","userName":"用户","userSign":"(周黑鸭)","message":"chaos","sub":[]}]